title: Living In The Post-Apocalyptic World, Beanie Babies, and You Can't Be A Big Brother
description:
What would the dinosaurs think of the humans that inherited their world? How fun is it to play with dry ice? Beanie Babies and spoiled children. The time John tried to be a Big Brother. Voicemails include: closed captions, Titanic and loud porn, TV blowjob, AITA: bartender obligations
